Surf_faceoff_remix_final
---------------------------------
My first release!

Old School map, like, donno, four years old, fun remake of it with nice ramps and nice lighting

Plays Better/Faster with more people!!

-Guns, Lots, Plus Ammo!
-Spawns 32+ (LOTS!)
-Small Size
-Fast, Intense Rounds
-1 Secret
-2 *hidden* xtra guns (m3 lots ammo, m249)
-3 spawns

Kept like original in many ways!
Worked for a few weeks on this off and on, i enjoyed it and hope you will to!
